### Get All Blogs
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog?page=1&limit=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Featured Blogs
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/featured
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Blog by Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/6977400b7154ad11ac52c242
Accept: application/json


###

### Create New Blog (with images)
POST {{baseUrl}}/blog
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My Test Blog
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

670f242b79f2f23f9ab61c9a
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="short_description"

This is a short summary.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Full blog description here...
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="thumbnail"; filename="thumbnail.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/thumbnail.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

